{
  "stem": "719.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "But I found them, which I'll let you know when we get there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "During the year, that one year from 1942 to '43, life, it wasn't good because you were a prisoner.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "But it was easier because we-- we learned to be productive, to do something, to maintain not to get sick.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "They didn't sort out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "They didn't make selections.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "There was no crematorium.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "It was a production.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "I compare it, basically-- except we didn't have husbands, and wives, and children like the Schindler people-- but I compare it in a way, it was a camp where if you could work, you were fine.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "You could manage to live as long as you didn't get in their way or you didn't act like you against them or lazy.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "That was our program.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "Just do what they tell you to do.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "During the year, there were a lot of non-Jewish people that used to work in those factories.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "They weren't allowed to come into the factory while this shift was going on.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "We had a shift, a separate shift, from the resident, from the workers that used to work before the war.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "But I do remember it was interesting that the previous people, like the previous woman that would operate the machine that I operate, if she would eat an apple, she would deliberately-- she wouldn't leave me the apple, but she would leave the skin of the apple, like she forgot to clean it up.",
      "word_count": 54
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "Or she would leave something in a cup.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "Sort of like-- and I realized what she's trying to do, but she was scared to help.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "But they did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And I heard from later on, when we went to our barracks, some girls would say, I had a treat today.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
